User rights in a team
=====================

Every memeber of a team have a set of rights inside the team 

 * Consult: The user can see informations relative to this team. Every memeber of a team can do this.
 * Talk: The user is allowed to express the team opinion.
 * Invite: The user can invite other people to join the team (private teams only)
 * Modify: The user can modify the team informations (contact, description ...)
 * Promote: the user can change the rights of the members of the team
 * Bank: The user can access and modify the team bank informations (he can also withdraw money from the team account)
